description.narrative: UNICEF was successful in influencing the initial steps of the new EDSP 2021-2030, which is child-centred. This resulted in a roadmap being agreed by MoET and key stakeholders that will ensure the rights of the most vulnerable children will be addressed in this EDSP. UNICEF supported a disability-inclusive Early Childhood Education Sector Analysis which will provide the roadmap with further measures on causes and how to include the most vulnerable children. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:31/12/2019
